{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-47","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbovao sam izgovor početnih glasova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da biste izgovorili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zh</span>, savijte vrh jezika nagore i unazad sve dok ne dosegne tvrdo nepce, potpuno blokirajući protok vazduha. Zatim, povucite jezik malo unazad kako biste stvorili uski prolaz. Izdišite kroz ovaj prolaz bez preterivog duva kako biste proizveli stabilan, vibrirajući zvuk koji počinje odmah.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zh</span> prati završna slova <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zha</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhe</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhu</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhu</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Пиньинь</th>\n<th>Херуфи</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhū</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">猪</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhú</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">竹</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhǔ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">主</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhù</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">住</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-